window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The vampires have always feared the first of their kind and his descendants. Now all immortals know there’s a new Eirikrson threatening their way of life.</p> <p>And they don’t intend to let her.<br> </p> <p>Catherine Stormhale has spent decades trying to crawl out of her family’s shadow. Now they’re calling her back home, to serve their clan against her new friends, and she has a choice to make.<br> </p> <p>Bash used to know who he was. A protector. A provider. A huntsman.</p> <p>After being bitten by a feral vampire and turned into a blood-craving thing, he’s lost everything. Family, purpose, honor.<br> </p> <p>When students are attacked outside of the institute, all warriors are called to help secure their borders.</p> <p>Bash and Cat sign up for the same schedule. He’s a newborn vampire with no control over his thirst and she, a princess born to this life.</p> <p>Neither knows what they’re in for.</p>"; 
